license.comment: This link is to the project Github, not to a license file. While some of the repos under this project use GPL, some use Apache. The link should be directly to the License file.

SDG[1].comment: This provides the same evidence used to justify SDG 1. While decreasing poverty can be assumed to decrease hunger as well, this project is targeted at the former.

SDG[2].comment: As with SDG 2, the evidence cited makes no direct mention of health initiatives.

documentation.comment: Quickstart has @TODO marks, no actual instructions. Documentation appears to be incomplete.
